#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:4
msgid "Scripting & Security"
msgstr "脚本与安全"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:6
msgid ""
"The ability to include Python scripts within blend-files is valuable for "
"advanced tasks such as rigging, automation and using the Game Engine. "
"However, it poses a security risk since Python does not restrict what a "
"script can do."
msgstr ""
"blend文件中包含Python脚本的能力在进阶任务如绑定、自动化和使用游戏引擎中是很有"
"价值的。然而，由于Python并没有严格限制脚本的行为也带来了一些安全风险。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:10
msgid "Therefore, you should only run scripts from sources you know and trust."
msgstr "因此，你应当只运行你知道且信赖的来源的脚本。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:12
msgid ""
"Automatic execution is disabled by default, however, some blend-files need "
"this to function properly."
msgstr ""
"自动运行脚本选项默认是禁用的，但是一些blend文件需要启用该选项才能正常工作。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:15
msgid ""
"When a blend-file tries to execute a script and is not allowed, a message "
"will appear in the header with the option to **Reload Trusted** or "
"**Ignore** the message."
msgstr ""
"当blend文件试图运行脚本并且未被允许，标题栏将显示信息，并提供 **重新加载受信"
"任(脚本)** 或者 **忽略** 该消息的选项。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:20
msgid "Info Header."
msgstr "信息标题栏"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:24
msgid "Scripts in Blend Files"
msgstr "blend文件中的脚本"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:27
msgid "Auto Execution"
msgstr "自动运行"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:29
msgid "Here are the different ways blend-files may automatically run scripts."
msgstr "下面是一些blend文件可能自动运行脚本的方式。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:31
msgid "Registered Text-Blocks"
msgstr "注册的文本块"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:32
msgid ""
"A text block can have its *Register* option enabled which means it will load "
"on start."
msgstr "文本块可以启用 *注册* 选项，这意味会在启动时自动加载。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:33
msgid "Animation Drivers"
msgstr "动画驱动"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:34
msgid ""
"Python expressions can be used to *Drive* values and are often used in more "
"advanced rigs and animations."
msgstr "Python表达式可以用于 *驱动* 值，并且经常在进阶的绑定和动画中使用。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:37
msgid "Game Engine Auto-Start"
msgstr "游戏引擎自动启动"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:36
msgid ""
"Scripts are often used for game logic, blend-files can have *Auto Start* "
"enabled with runs the game on load."
msgstr ""
"脚本经常用于游戏逻辑，blend文件可以启用 *自动启动* 选项，加载后自动运行游戏。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:40
msgid "Manual Execution"
msgstr "手动运行"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:42
msgid ""
"There are other ways scripts in a blend-file may execute that require user "
"interaction (therefore will run even when auto-execution is off), but you "
"should be aware that this is the case since it is not necessarily obvious."
msgstr ""
"还有一些情况下，blend文件需要用户交互才能运行脚本(因此禁用自动运行也会运行)，"
"但你需要清楚这种情形，因为它不是那么显而易见。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:47
msgid "Running a script in the text editor."
msgstr "在文本编辑器中运行脚本"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:48
msgid ""
"Rendering with FreeStyle, because FreeStyle uses scripts to control line "
"styles."
msgstr "使用FreeStyle 渲染，由于 FreeStyle 使用脚本控制线条样式。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:49
msgid "Running the Game Engine."
msgstr "运行游戏引擎"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:53
msgid "Controlling Script Execution"
msgstr "控制脚本运行"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:55
msgid ""
"Blender provides a number of ways to control whether scripts from a blend-"
"file are allowed to automatically execute."
msgstr "Blender提供了一些用于控制是否允许blend文件中脚本自动运行的方法。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:58
msgid ""
"First of all, the File Browser has the option **Trusted Source** which you "
"can use on a case-by-case basis to control auto-execution."
msgstr "首先，文件浏览器有 **受信任来源** 选项，可以用于逐个控制自动运行。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:61
msgid ""
"However, you may forget to set this, or open a file without going through "
"the File Browser -- so you can change the default (described next)."
msgstr ""
"不过，你可能会忘记设置这个选项，或者不通过文件浏览器打开文件 -- 所以你可以改"
"变默认选项(下面继续说明)。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:67
msgid "Setting Defaults"
msgstr "设置默认值"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:69
msgid ""
"In the *File* tab of the User Preferences, there is the toggle :ref:`Auto "
"Run Python Scripts <prefs-auto-execution>`."
msgstr ""
"在用户设置的 *文件* 选项卡中，有  :ref:`自动运行Python脚本 <prefs-auto-"
"execution>` 的选项。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:72
msgid ""
"This means the **Trusted Source** option in the File Browser will be enabled "
"by default, and scripts can run when blend-files are loaded without using "
"the File Browser."
msgstr ""
"这意味着文件浏览器中的 **受信任来源** 选项会默认启用，并且无需通过文件浏览"
"器，blend文件加载后，脚本就可以自动运行。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:75
msgid ""
"Once enabled you have the option to exclude certain directories, a typical "
"configuration would be to trust all paths except for the download directory."
msgstr "一旦启用，你可以排除特定目录，典型的配置是信任除下载目录外的所有路径。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:80
msgid "Auto Run Python Scripts"
msgstr "自动运行Python脚本"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:84
msgid "Command Line"
msgstr "命令行"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:86
msgid ""
"You may want to perform batch rendering or some other task from the command "
"line -- running Blender without an interface."
msgstr ""
"你可能想要从命令行执行批处理渲染或一些其他的任务 — 不使用界面运行Blender。"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:89
msgid ""
"In this case, the User Preferences are still used but you may want to "
"override them:"
msgstr "这种情况下，前面的用户设置同样适用，不过你也许想要覆盖该设置："

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:91
msgid "Enable with ``-y`` or ``--enable-autoexec``"
msgstr "使用 ``-y`` or ``--enable-autoexec`` 启用"

#: ../../manual/advanced/scripting/security.rst:92
msgid "Disable with ``-Y`` or ``--disable-autoexec``"
msgstr "使用 ``-Y`` or ``--disable-autoexec`` 禁用"

